code: @Ignore(value = "Can only be run manually after generating and compiling code from other generators") @Test public void testExecute() throws Exception {     // delete target file to begin     final File outDir = new File("target/site/cameldocs").     final File outFile = new File(outDir, "TestComponent.html").     if (outFile.exists()) {         outFile.delete().     }     final DocumentGeneratorMojo mojo = new DocumentGeneratorMojo().     configureGeneratorMojo(mojo).     mojo.setDestDir("cameldocs").     mojo.setReportOutputDirectory(outDir.getParentFile()).     mojo.execute().     // check target file was generated     assertExists(outFile). }
